# Workflow

## Live Rebuild

Before editing any `.typ` file, ensure `make watch` is running so changes compile automatically.

1. Check if a PID file exists at `build/watch.pid` and whether that process is still alive.
2. If not running, start it in the background and record the PID:

```bash
make watch &
echo $! > build/watch.pid
```

3. Do not start a second watcher if one is already active.
